title: Westwood 3 Bed / 3 Bath Apt + Parking, Kitchen Appliances
posting_body: ['3 bedroom 3 bath apartment in the heart of Westwood available for this School Year.', 'Apartment with gorgeous views, laminate wood flooring and a gas fireplace.', 'Gourmet kitchen is equipped with a dishwasher, a gas stove, and a refrigerator.', "At Ashton Towers, you'll enjoy a comfortable life of luxury and relaxation.", 'Our residents are offered full access to all our exquisite community amenities.', "From swimming pool, fitness center and gorgeous panoramic views of the Westwood skyline, you'll find easy living with endless comforts and conveniences here at Ashton Towers.", 'We pride ourselves on ensuring residents only the best in apartment living.', 'We are perfectly situated in a very cosmopolitan neighborhood, our convenient location puts you within walking distance of everything in Westwood Village, just one block south of Wilshire and one block west of Westwood Boulevard, exactly where you want to be!', 'For appointment or for questions, call us at', 'show contact info', '.', 'For more property photos, floor plans or to apply, visit <URL>', '10930 Ashton Avenue', 'Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024', 'Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills', '3 bedroom apartment offers the following amenities:', 'Tile Flooring', 'Central Air/Heating', 'Laminate Wood Flooring', 'Cozy Gas Fireplace', 'Cable Available', 'Dishwasher', 'Stove And Oven', 'Refrigerator', 'Microwave', 'Vertical Blinds', 'Mirrored Closet Doors', 'Spectacular Views Available', 'Community Amenities:', 'Rooftop Swimming Pool', 'Covered Parking', 'Elevator', 'Garage', 'Extra Storage', 'Spa Access', 'Fitness Center', 'Assigned Parking', 'Beautiful Landscaping', 'Disclaimer: Pictures are a representation but may not be of the exact apartment.', 'Advertised unit availability, rental rates, and terms are updated every 24 hours and conditions are subject to change without notice.', 'Please call for latest availability details.']
